rows.label: xs99110120_MSG0001
rows.name: Linly! Linly! What is Linly making?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110120_MSG0002
rows.name: Today's one of my specialties: pot pie.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110120_MSG0003
rows.name: Pie? Did Tatsu ever tell Linly pie is his favorite?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110120_MSG0004
rows.name: Tatsu will even help Linly make it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110120_MSG0005
rows.name: Great! Why don't you flatten out that crust.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110120_MSG0007
rows.name: How big does Linly want crust to be?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110120_MSG0010
rows.name: Meh! How many times Tatsu need to tell Linly?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110120_MSG0011
rows.name: Tatsu is here to serve, not BE served![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110120_MSG0012
rows.name: Oh riiight. That does sound familiar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110120_MSG0013
rows.name: Linly always say that, too! Linly say that every time![ST:wait ]
